负责任的国家应认识到，在世界卫生大会上排除 2400 万人的利益只会危及而不是推进共同的全球卫生目标。 随后，「台湾驻美代表处」也转发并置顶了布林肯的声明，对美国的支持表示感谢。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-0d182dbb147a0c951e802ebf00700ea4_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "36 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/458323936"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I7860grjwhtcqEAMaCDY0MTMwMDkzIJbv14QGMCQ4/gVAKXIJNDU4MzIzOTM2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "42_1620576332.598456", "card_id": "Q_312216212", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 107}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "高中英语刷题有用吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "高中每天中午刷题有用吗，这些时间是否可以用来干其他的事"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-9257c9cd9c48f6dfe1cb0144d3d1fe5d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "34 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/312216212"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I7860grjwhtcqEAMaCDMxNjU4MDgwIKuPlOMFMAE4qARAKnIJMzEyMjE2MjEyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "43_1620576332.5988436", "card_id": "Q_267880033", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 64}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些好看又不贵的日系风格短袖 T 恤推荐？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "各位知乎的大佬们，夏天要到了，有那种好看又不怎么贵的日系风格短袖或者 T 恤推荐吗？ 等等，你们是不是有什么误解，题主是个男孩子…"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-e368854aa5906c16fe6c6628f722a9db_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "31 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/267880033"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I7860grjwhtcqEAMaCDIxNTg1MjcwIKqK1dQFMAE47gxAK3IJMjY3ODgwMDMzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "44_1620576332.5992765", "card_id": "Q_27251347", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 53}, "tar